| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2671 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6c1c5d24-883b-5a48-b8e8-07bb3d04f485"
